text: Thomas Chambers (20 November 1931 - 8 June 2015) was a South African cricketer. He played one first-class match for Eastern Province in 1956/57. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1931 births Category:2015 deaths Category:South African cricketers Category:Eastern Province cricketers Category:Cricketers from Cape Town
